source.sqlReaderQuery:
SELECT 
	ItemCode,
	ISNULL(FrgnName, ItemName) AS ItemName, 
	CardCode, 
	ItmsGrpCod, 
	U_ServiceItem,
	DB_NAME() AS [DB_NAME],
        U_PORF,
	cast ( LastPurPrc  as float) LastPurPrc   ,
	LastPurDat ,
	LastPurCur 
 FROM [dbo].[OITM]

WHERE frozenFor = 'N'
AND PrchseItem = 'Y'
AND U_PORF = 'Y'

SELECT 
	ItemCode,
	ISNULL(FrgnName, ItemName) AS ItemName, 
	CardCode, 
	ItmsGrpCod, 
	U_ServiceItem,
	DB_NAME() AS [DB_NAME],
        U_PORF,
	cast ( LastPurPrc  as float) LastPurPrc   ,
	LastPurDat ,
	LastPurCur 
 FROM [dbo].[OITM]

WHERE frozenFor = 'N'
AND PrchseItem = 'Y'
AND U_PORF = 'Y'
